gov.sandia.cognition.framework.learning.converter

Class CogxelDoubleConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.sandia.cognition.framework.learning.converter.CogxelDoubleConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CogxelConverter<java.lang.Double>, CloneableSerializable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class CogxelDoubleConverter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CogxelConverter<java.lang.Double>
    The CogxelDoubleConverter class converts a Cogxel to and from a double value by using its activation.

    2.0
    Author:
